i'm looking for some good apple pie recipes know any crunchy carmel apple pie ingredients for the pie pastry crust for a deep dish pie inch homemade or store bought cup sugar tbsp all purpose flour tsp ground cinnamon tsp salt cups thinly sliced peeled apples golden delicious and fuji apples recipe crumb topping cup chopped pecans cup caramel topping ingredients for the crumb topping cup packed brown sugar cup all purpose flour cup quick cooking rolled oats cup butter directions for the crumb topping stir together brown sugar flour rolled oats cut in cup butter until topping is like course crumbs set aside directions for the pie in a large mixing bowl stir together the sugar flour cinnamon and salt add apple slices and gently toss until coated transfer apple mixture to the pie shell i remove the store bought pie shell from the aluminum pie plate and transfer it to a inch pie plate of my own but you do not have to sprinkle crumb topping over apple mixture place pie on a cookie sheet so the drippings don't drop into your oven cover edges of pie with aluminum foil bake in a preheated oven for minutes then remove foil and put back in for another to minutes without foil remove from oven sprinkle pie with chopped pecans then drizzle with caramel on top cool on a wire rack and enjoy warm or at room temperature delicious recipe enjoy Puff pastry Coffee Cuisine of Denmark Jewish cuisine Japanese cuisine Pizza Cold Stone Creamery Cuisine of the Philippines Apple pie Bacon Tofu Rice pudding French fries Halva Barbecue Brewery Cuisine of Brazil Cuisine of the Southern United States Baklava Pie Baked Alaska Apple Bagel Potato Cooking weights and measures Pancake Cajun cuisine Chocolate Hot dog Ice cream Breakfast Haggis Recipe Dim sum Cookie Hamburger Cookware and bakeware D__ner kebab Chili con carne Soul food Muffin Pop-Tarts Dumpling Sushi German cuisine Alice B. Toklas brownie Vinegar Custard Toffee Cake Mince pie Flour Ramen French toast French cuisine Bengali cuisine Chees